terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport offers check-in, waiting areas, and boarding gates for all flights.

terminals.name: Seaplane Terminal
terminals.description: The seaplane terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport is where seaplanes take off and land on the water.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport handles all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is used for general aviation and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network by selecting 'BFI Airport WiFi' from the list of available networks.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves mainly Alaska Airlines flights.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves mainly international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
